# Core Product Rules

- Flagship: KXBTC15M (Kalshi BTC 15-min), Mystic-style launch wedge.
- Secondary: BTC hourly, weather markets, sports/event systems.
- Modes: paper -> safe-live -> live. Never skip safe-live.
- Restart-safe: all execution state persisted.
- Accounting: fees, slippage, corrections reconciled vs exchange.
- Authoritative refs: docs/pdfs/ and docs/ARCHITECTURE-ZEROTRADING-CORE.md.
- FSM / accounting deviations require DECISION-LOG entry.
- Any bug found or fixed MUST be logged in `ai/summaries/CRASH-AND-FIX-LOG.md` before the session ends. Include commit hash. Also log in the child repo (`meszaroszack/zerotradingx15minbtc`) if relevant.
- Read `ai/summaries/CRASH-AND-FIX-LOG.md` before writing any code — it lists every known crash and pattern.
